{"/service/ndnp/vnstcsc/batch_vnstcsc_enighed_ver01/data/sn84037526/00414180012/1930101701/0961.xml":{"full_text":"CHRISTIANSTED THEATRE\n845 SUNDAY NIGHT 8.45\n815 MONDAY NIGH'! 8.15\nCOME ARND SEE!I! .....covevivee. URE AND IIEARI\nSophie Tucker, Vaudeville headliner, Musical comedy star and ectertainer of royalty in\n66 o\nHONKY TONK\na Warner Bros. all-talking and singing picture that gets over the top, BIG everywhere,\n**Honky lonk\u2019\u2019 is declared to be \u201c\u2018iu every sense a feminine parallel to *'The Sing\ning Fool\u2019\u201d and it\u2019s good for Al that he got his picture out ahead of Sophie\u2019s\u2019\u2019\nSophie is as good at any point in her picture as Jolson is at any poiot in ais, and\nbetter as to point for point ayerage. (so much for comparisons).\nSophie sings, Oh yes, she sings several songs, old and new songs, and when she\nsings \u2018\u2018Some of these days\u2019\u2019......well, perhaps you have not heard good singing, but\nbelieve it or believe it not, \u2018you ain\u2019t heard nothin\u2019 yet\u2019\u2019,\nYou\u2019il no doubt like to konow that Lila Lee is the star\u2019s daughter in the picture,\nMahlon Hamilton is the reliable male friend, that Mamma has made a lady of the giri\nby making a bum of herself and the little lady don\u2019t thank Mamma ete. ete.,....but the\ncrux of the picture is Sophie, \u201c\u2018lf you knew Sophie as I know Sophie\u2019\u2019....well you will\nknow her if you see \u2018\u2018Honky Tonk\u2019 and if you don\u2019t see \u2018\u2018Honky :I'onk\u2019 it\u2019s your\nfuneral, not ours\nEngage your tickets ahead of time please and sead fur them at th: thea ro (Coris\ntiansted) on Sunday afternvon from 4 p. m.\nADMISSION 50c. AND 25\u00a2c.\nLOCAL\nSome persons don\u2019t seem to be in\nclined to look with serious eyes or the\nway things are drifting in this island,\nfeeling thet the pr2sent economic un\nrest may return to vcormal in time. It\nmay just as well be undersiood ncw\nand we may